text: Mimulopsis arborescens is a tree from the family Acanthaceae and a species of the genus Mimulopsis. This tree is one of the species that can be found at Rwenzori Mountains. ==References== ==External links== * Category:Acanthaceae Category:Flora of East Tropical Africa Category:Flora of South Tropical Africa Category:Flora of West-Central Tropical Africa
title: Mimulopsis arborescens
